===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|abime}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{m|fro|abisme}} from {{etyl|LL.|en}} {{m|la|*abyssimus}}, a superlative of {{m|la|abyssus||bottomless pit}}, from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{m|grc|ἄβυσσος}}. Cognate to {{etyl|fr|en}} {{m|fr|abîme}}. See also {{m|en|abyss}}.<ref name=OCD>{{R:OCD2|page=6}}</ref><ref name=SOED>{{R:SOED5|page=11}}</ref>

